;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新聞來源連結:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60273334%3Futm_source%3D01appshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=34ff30f1f6bcb38a1fcd9ee415fb6282&amp;amp;fid=54" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32024917&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1108&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-09-05T08:48:34+08:00</published></entry></feed>